Author: lavenderily
Text: I’m sorry :( I feel your pain. Weight gain doesn’t happen for everyone with every medication. I’m also on Effexor but I didn’t experience weight gain until I started the Prozac. Hopefully you’ll be ok. If not, just remember you can always get off of it if you need to. But make sure you don’t cut cold turkey—talk to your doctor first. ❤️❤️

Author: jfc-im-dying
Text: I just started Zoloft and I’m so terrified of the weight gain that it’s made me nauseous, making me not eat lol :/
